steps.html_instructions: Head west on N St toward Rogers Memorial Dr
Merge onto US-77 N/Homestead Expy via the ramp to I-80
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-80 W and merge onto I-80 W

Turn left onto NE-44 S/2nd Ave
Continue to follow NE-44 S

Turn right onto NE-44 S/US-34 W/US-6 W
Continue to follow US-34 W/US-6 W

Turn left onto US-183 S/Burlington St
Continue to follow US-183 S
Entering Kansas

Turn left onto Co Rd 31/Co Ln 31
Continue to follow Co Rd 31

Turn right onto CO-109 S/Grand Ave
Continue to follow CO-109 S

Continue onto US-350 W/Potter Dr
Continue to follow US-350 W

Turn right onto Hwy 160 Bypass/160 Hwy Bypass
Continue to follow 160 Hwy Bypass

Turn left to merge onto I-25 S
Entering New Mexico
Turn right onto NM-466 N/Old Pecos Trail (signs for Historic US 66)
